      "html": "<p>15世纪中期，来自 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of thunder \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/thunder\">thunder</a>（n.）和 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of bolt \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/bolt\">bolt</a>（n.）“箭头，抛射物”。</p>"
